  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA9">
<l>kaṇṇuṅ kamalaṅ kamalamē kaittalamu</l>
<l>maṇṇaḷanta pātamu maṟṟavaiyē – yeṇṇiṟ</l>
<l>karumā mukilvaṇṇaṉ kārkkaṭaṉīr vaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>ṟirumā maṇivaṇṇaṉ ṟēcu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The eyes lotuses, and just lotuses, the palms of [his] hands,</l>
<l>and [his] feet that measured the earth again<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">Here the the particle maṟṟu emphasises the change of subject, while avai acts anaphorically for the third mention of lotus.</note> are such. – Immeasurable</l>
<l>light [is] he, the colour of big black clouds, he the colour of the rain ocean’s water,</l>
<l>he the colour of brilliant dark sapphire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
